WEBVTT

00:00.525 --> 00:02.161
I'm awesome at multitasking.

00:05.057 --> 00:05.862
Um, maybe not.

00:06.581 --> 00:11.521
Apparently, the average student uses 10 to 40 percent of their study time on digital distractions.

00:11.995 --> 00:15.219
It's no surprise that some of us need help to minimize distractions.

00:16.146 --> 00:18.145
Here are some tips to help you find some balance.

00:19.207 --> 00:22.760
The first step is admitting you have a problem.

00:24.273 --> 00:25.757
Try something like RescueTime.

00:25.973 --> 00:29.715
It tracks your online history to see when and where you're wasting the most time.

00:30.873 --> 00:32.523
Now that you know the nature of your vice,...

00:32.842 --> 00:37.198
...you can set limits for yourself with a variety of different tools like these.

00:37.604 --> 00:41.139
These browser extensions can limit or block your access to certain sites.

